content.description: Start on the lowest huge jug and head straight up.  Too easy for a warmup.
content.location:
In the west forest on Outkast Boulders.  Just to the right of

Humble Mumble

.

content.description:
Start at lowest finger crack far to the right.  Head up the lip and to the left using the thin seam.  Same topout as

B.O.B

.
content.location:
In West Forest about 70 meters above the obelisk boulder.  To the right of

B.O.B

.

content.description:
SDS start same as

Aquemini

way in the cave but come out to the left onto a slimper and make a huge move to a bad crimper.  Match hands and make another huge move to a nice hold.  Top out.
content.location:
On the Outkast Boulders in the west forest.  Same start as

Aquemini

.

content.description: SDS on opposing sidepulls and head straight up and top out.
content.location:
On Outkast boulders and on the same boulder as

Aquemini

, but to the right of it.  In West Forest about 75 meters up above the Obelisk Boulder.

content.description: SDS in cave.  Start in the horizontal roof crack as far back as you can go.  Climb out of the roof and hit the lip.  Traverse up the lip to the right.  The moves get easier as you get higher.  For a little easier way up try heading right after coming out of the cave along slopers.  Then head up and finish as the original.  The Lip has cooler moves but the slopers are super fun as well.
content.location:
In the West Foreston the Outkast Boulders. Approximately 80 meters above and a little to the west of the Obelisk Boulder and the

High Warm Up

.  About 30 meters above

Underclings and Sidepulls

.  Follow large trail of boulders till you come across this problem.
